User launches program and starts with his man at a predetermined location in a grid of dirt, empty pathways, and emarald/dirt blocks.
After two seconds, an enemy will appear in the upper right hand corner and move towards the player throught the pathways.
Every five seconds after that another enemy appears.
Enemies are slightly faster than the player.
Enemies can randomly turn into a nobbin which will attack the player in sytraight line and dig dirt and collect emeralds.  He is slower.
The player can shoot a bullet that kills enemies.